<h1>Welcome!</h1>

<h2>New to Volity?</h2>

<p>
The best way to start is by jumping in and playing some games! <a href="/games/gamut/">Download a copy of Gamut</a>, our client software, to enter the world of Volity gaming.
</p>
<h2>What is Volity?</h2>

<p>
Volity is an open platform for real-time, multiplayer, Internet-based
games. By "open", we mean not just that anyone can create player
accounts and start playing games, but also that anyone can develop and
add their own games to it! <a href="about.html">Read More...</a>
</p>

<hr />

